ygData.messageBody:
glad to hear from you :) i dont know about the servers that any
particular bears might play on, i know i am a cub that plays on bristle
bane, but that is beside the point, this list is a bit slow, but we have
got quite a few good bits of information from it i am really glad i
joined it myself. i have a tendency to be more of a lurker myself unless
it is to greet someone, i always try to greet the new comers :) anyways,
some one else should be able to answer your question, good luck in your
adventures and have fun :)

Redspider
23rd circle rogue of the circle of unseen hands, of the order of the
dawn.

> Greetings, EQers:

>
> I live in St. Louis, am a 34 year old Bear employed as a statistician
> and research designer for a managed health company. Chris is an LA

> together now for just over a year, hopefully to be together a
> lifetime or two.
>
> Glad I found the list. I'd love to hear from you folks!
> Jack
